      <li>You are strictly forbidden from contacting any developer within our network for employment or contracts outside of RipplePop's knowledge and oversight. Contracting or paying our team for work completed outside the service offering from RipplePop will result in a fine equal to the yearly salary of that RipplePop team member.</li>
      <li>Each provision of this Agreement will be considered severable, such that if any one provision or clause conflicts with existing or future applicable law or may not be given full effect because of such law, no other provision that can operate without the conflicting provision or clause will be affected.</li>
